y'all took last night.

47
00:03:26,457 --> 00:03:29,000
- Well, it could've been worse.
- What'd you say?

48
00:03:30,544 --> 00:03:33,922
- Could've been worse.
- Yeah.

49
00:03:34,006 --> 00:03:36,466
You could say that
about nearly everything, I guess.

50
00:03:36,550 --> 00:03:39,010
[Engine Rumbling]

51
