01:45:12,682 --> 01:45:15,309
That Logan boy's
a quarterback now, ain't he?

1474
01:45:15,393 --> 01:45:18,103
Boy, we finally got us a team.

1475
01:45:18,188 --> 01:45:20,481
Didn't back in your day,
did they, Sonny?

1476
01:45:20,565 --> 01:45:22,316
Nah, we wasn't much good.

1477
01:45:22,400 --> 01:45:24,651
Well, you just never learned
the fundamentals...

1478
01:45:24,736 --> 01:45:29,323
you know, blocking and tackling...
not like this team.

1479
01:45:29,407 --> 01:45:31,825
- When was it you graduated?
- Last year.

1480
01:45:31,910 --> 01:45:33,410
You don't mean it?

1481
01:45:33,495 --> 01:45:36,705
Seems like longer than that
since you and old Duane played ball.

1482
01:45:36,789 --> 01:45:39,541
I seen old Duane a while ago.
He's home on leave.

1483
01:45:39,626 --> 01:45:43,504
- Wearin' his uniform.
- I ain't seen him yet.

1484
01:45:43,588 --> 01:45:45,672
- ## [Continues]
- [Cheering]

1485
01:45:45,757 --> 01:45:48,592
