01:47:06,838 --> 01:47:08,171
[Door Opens]

1501
01:47:09,257 --> 01:47:12,342
- Hi. How you been?
- Oh, pretty good.

1502
01:47:15,513 --> 01:47:18,265
Yeah, I been thinking all week
that, you know, I'd run into you.

1503
01:47:18,349 --> 01:47:20,892
Yeah.

1504
01:47:20,977 --> 01:47:22,894
I heard you was going off to Korea.

1505
01:47:22,979 --> 01:47:25,939
I thought I'd better get over here
and see you before you got off.

1506
01:47:26,024 --> 01:47:28,108
Glad you did.

1507
01:47:28,192 --> 01:47:30,110
I'm taking the bus out
early in the morning.

1508
01:47:30,194 --> 01:47:32,029
Oh.

1509
01:47:36,618 --> 01:47:39,119
Thought you might want to go
to the picture show.

1510
01:47:39,203 --> 01:47:42,539
Miss Mosey's having to close it.
Tonight's the last night.

1511
01:47:42,624 --> 01:47:46,960
Yeah, might as well go.
Hate to miss the last night.

1512
01:47:47,045 --> 01:47:50,964
Take the Mercury. Be the last chance
I'll have to drive it for a while.

