I ain't over her yet.

1570
01:51:43,072 --> 01:51:45,073
It's the damndest thing.

1571
01:51:47,869 --> 01:51:49,995
That's the only reason, uh...

1572
01:51:50,079 --> 01:51:52,581
the only reason you and I
got into it that time, you know.

1573
01:51:54,625 --> 01:51:56,710
Reckon she likes it down in Dallas?

1574
01:51:56,794 --> 01:51:59,379
It's hard to say.
Maybe she does.

1575
01:52:01,090 --> 01:52:02,716
[Deep Breath]

1576
01:52:02,800 --> 01:52:05,969
You reckon you and her would have got it all
straighted out if I hadn't have butted in?

1577
01:52:06,053 --> 01:52:08,305
Oh, no.

1578
01:52:08,389 --> 01:52:10,223
No.
[Sighs]

1579
01:52:10,308 --> 01:52:12,350
No. They'd have annulled me, too,
even if we had.

1580
01:52:15,313 --> 01:52:20,317
Y'all, uh... Y'all never even
got into the motel?

1581
01:52:20,401 --> 01:52:22,152
No.

1582
01:52:26,407 --> 01:52:27,908
Well.

1583
01:52:28,951 --> 01:52:31,202
Better get on before we both freeze.

1584
01:52:41,505 --> 01:52:43,423
Here are the keys.

1585
01:52:45,009 --> 01:52:46,968
- So long, buddy.
- So long, Duane.

1586
01:52:48,137 --> 01:52:49,846
Be careful.

1587
01:52:49,931 --> 01:52:51,890
I'll take care of the Mercury for you.

1588
01:52:51,974 --> 01:52:53,975
I'll see you in a year or two
if I don't get shot.

1589
01:53:14,997 --> 01:53:17,666
[Wind Blowing Outside]

1590
01:53:30,304 --> 01:53:34,224
[Horn Honks, Brakes Squeal]

1591
01:53:51,742 --> 01:53:54,244
[Wind Blowing]

1592
01:54:19,437 --> 01:54:22,480
[Cattle Mooing, Hooves Clattering]

1593
01:54:24,275 --> 01:54:27,652
[Men Chattering]

1594
01:54:27,737 --> 01:54:29,696
[Man]
He run right out in front of that station.

1595
01:54:29,780 --> 01:54:31,865
Christ, he didn't...
Trucker didn't have a chance.

1596
01:54:31,949 --> 01:54:33,992
[Man #2] Yeah, he's out here
all the time doin' something.

1597
01:54:34,076 --> 01:54:37,787
- [Cattle Mooing, Hooves Clattering]
- [Sheriff] I could see it wasn't your fault.

1598
01:54:37,872 --> 01:54:40,665
